name: Cash Cow 2
description:
It’s classic puzzler fun! Remove groups of milk bottles to score big and fill the level bar! Watch out for cracked bottles that can spoil your day! Get this Webkinz World favorite for your iPhone or iPod Touch!
Earn Kinzcash™ while you play! Store and send KinzCash earnings to your active Webkinz World account whenever you have an internet connection. Now you can earn KinzCash while you're on a vacation, in the car, or just hanging out in the backyard.
Also check out these additional great Webkinz World games for your iPhone and iPod Touch: Polar Plunge, Goober’s Lab and Smoothie Moves!
For more information on Webkinz, visit webkinz.com.
